bundles.name: FREEDOM_PACKAGE
bundles.description: A mortgage package offering interest rate savings and fee waivers on the home loan and other financial services.

fees.name: ACCOUNT_SERVICE_FEE_-_HOME_LOAN_PLUS
fees.additionalInfo: Payble to levy costs we incur in provding your account and its service

fees.name: ESTABLISHMENT_FEE_-_HOME_LOAN_PLUS
fees.additionalInfo: To cover our costs associated with establishing your loan

fees.name: PACKAGE_FEE_-_FREEDOM_PACKAGE
fees.additionalInfo: Annual mortgage package fee entitles you to benefits such as discounts & fee waivers on your home loan or line of credit, transaction accounts, credit card, insurance etc.

fees.name: BASIC_VARIATION_FEE
fees.additionalInfo: Payable when we process your request to change or restructure your repayment

fees.name: COMPLEX_VARIATION_FEE
fees.additionalInfo: Payable when we process your request that varaies your product, security, interest rate or repayment type, unless switching to Principal & Interest payments.

fees.name: PRINCIPAL_INCREASE_FEE
fees.additionalInfo: Payable when we process your request to increase the principal amount of your loan

fees.name: PROGRESS_PAYMENT_FEE
fees.additionalInfo: Payable on the first drawdown after settlement to cover the administration costs of progress payments for your construction or home renovation.

fees.name: RATE_LOCK_FEE
fees.additionalInfo: If you elect to lock-in a fixed interest rate prior to commencement of the fixed rate term

fees.name: DEFAULT_ADMINISTRATION_FEE
fees.additionalInfo: Payable if there is an event of default under the terms of your loan

fees.name: MORTGAGE_OFFSET_ADMINISTRATION_FEE
fees.additionalInfo: Payable when we link your qualifying loan to a qualifying deposit account to provide mortgage offset. Waived for Freedom Package.

fees.name: RTGS_''SAME_DAY''_PAYMENT
fees.additionalInfo: Payable when you request a high value, time critical payment from your account to another financial instituation on a real time basis for "same day" payment

fees.name: REDRAW_FEE
fees.additionalInfo: Payable when we manually process your request (eg: in Branch) to redraw available advance funds from your loan account. Excluse online redraws.
